Many Ghâsh-hai Orcs prowl the halls of Ânghumu-ru. These fire-loving enemy forces should be defeated.
Ghâsh-hai Orcs can be found in Ânghumu-ru, in the north-west quadrant of the Flaming Deeps.\n\nThese fire-loving enemy forces should be defeated.
You have defeated a number of Orcs at Ânghumu-ru, sapping the strength of their armies and assuring that they will pose less of a threat to the dwarves of the Flaming Deeps.
